1583, "(fr)Terrans and Vasudans cruiser groups meet in a stand off.  Multiplayer mission.  Max respawns 10.  Recommended respawns 5."

1584, "(fr)Terran Command has initiated Operation Fury, a renewed offensive against Shivan positions in the Capella system.  Phase 1: eliminate all hostiles and secure the Vega system.  Reconnaissance has located a Hammer of Light cruiser group, comprised of two Aten-class warships, en route to the Beta Aquilae jump node.  Our task force has been deployed to engage and destroy this threat.  The Fenris-class Mjollnir and the Leviathan-class Dionysos will provide support for the assault."

1585, "(fr)Sensors indicate a Terran cruiser group on intercept course.  Engage and destroy the Mjollnir and Dionysos warships."

1586, "(fr)Our task force secured the Vega system, and Command has issued the go-ahead for Phase 2 of Operation Fury.  Excellent work, pilot."

1587, "(fr)You destroyed only one Aten warship.  Command has suspended Operation Fury until a more proficient force can secure the Vega system.  Anything less than total victory is unacceptable."

1588, "(fr)Guard your bombers and keep your wingmen focused."

1589, "(fr)Because of your failure, Command has scrapped Operation Fury.  With officers like you, the alliance needs no enemies."

1590, "(fr)Hammer of Light destroyed the Mjollnir and the Dionysos.  You are grounded pending a full investigation.  Dismissed, pilot."

1591, "(fr)Excellent work, pilot.  You destroyed the Mjollnir and the Dionysos."

1592, "(fr)A Terran warship survived the battle.  You failed to destroy both cruisers."

1593, "(fr)The Mjollnir and the Dionysos survived the battle.  You failed to destroy the Terran cruisers."

1594, "(fr)Both Aten cruisers survived the Terran attack.  In the divine scrolls it is written: ''In the blood of my enemy, my hands are sanctified.''"

