1601, "(fr)GTA reconnaissance has located the Ragnarok, a GTI science vessel.  Researchers on board the Ragnarok are developing the Serkr warhead, a megabomb of tremendous destructive power.  GTI scientists are now in the process of developing a warhead-viable containment system for the Serkr's volatile core."

1602, "(fr)Your objective is to destroy the Ragnarok and its Orion-class escort, the Heimdall.  For the sake of the Terran-Vasudan alliance, the Serkr project must be terminated."

1603, "(fr)Outstanding, pilot!  You destroyed the Ragnarok and the Heimdall.  Your efforts have terminated the GTI's Serkr project."

1604, "(fr)You destroyed the Ragnarok and terminated the GTI's Serkr project.  Command regrets you failed to eliminate the Heimdall, but you achieved your primary objective."

1605, "(fr)You are a disgrace, pilot.  The Ragnarok and the Heimdall escaped.  If GTI succeeds in stabilizing the Serkr warhead, every capital ship in the Terran-Vasudan alliance will be at risk.  Dismissed."

1606, "(fr)Use the explosive power of the Ragnarok to your advantage.  Let it get close to the Heimdall before destroying it."

