1631, "(fr)The PVD Serket, a Typhon-class warship, has transmitted a distress call to allied forces in the Deneb system.  Two Lilith-class Shivan cruisers have engaged the Serket.  The Vasudan ship has sustained minor damage, but the Shivans have them outgunned.  Our mission: destroy the hostiles and save the Vasudan cruiser."

1632, "(fr)You saved the PVD Serket and obliterated the Shivans.  The Serket was able to complete its operations in the Deneb system, and the Vasudan admiralty has extended its gratitude.  Well done, pilot."

1633, "(fr)You neutralized the Shivan cruiser group, but the PVD Serket was destroyed.  Command has sent its regrets to the Vasudan admiralty.  Dismissed, pilot."

1634, "(fr)Use some wingmen to defend the Serket."

1635, "(fr)You are an embarrassment to the Terran fleet, pilot.  The Shivan destroyer vaporized the PVD Serket and escaped.  This failure may damage our alliance with the Vasudans, and you are grounded until further notice.  Dismissed."

