Scanning the transport and cargo is a little more difficult.  Get the transport as soon as you arrive, then order your wingmen to destroy the freighters so you can scan the cargo in relative peace.  Scan the cruisers last -- they aren't going anywhere."

3220, "(fr)This mission was a surprise for both of us, pilot.  Thanks to your scans, we have verified that the cruisers you encountered are GTI ships, originally registered as GTC Odin and GTC Thor.  Official records, however, show that these cruisers were destroyed in two separate engagements at the beginning of the Great War.  The fact that these ships were present in a highly sensitive sector of Shivan-controlled space at the same time as your deployment is more than a little suspicious.  We can only assume that this operation was carried out by a rogue element of the GTI."

